snippet.title: Hello Fangaming Collection - Trailer - Ten Years of Fangaming!
snippet.description:
Join Mario and Luigi on their adventure in this ten year anniversary collection! This collection includes an assortment of remastered levels handpicked from a wide variety of fangames released by Hello Fangaming between 2006-2016.

Download Game (Included in the Hello Fangaming Time Capsule)
https://www.indiedb.com/games/hello-fangaming-time-capsule-launcher/downloads/hello-fangaming-time-capsule

Music 1: Super Mario Concerto Part 3.1 by Kreepman
Music 2: A Twisted Carousel by steampianist
